It's sort of like a party.

02:29.399 --> 02:31.359
I really want to go.

02:31.401 --> 02:34.029
Well, your family is having

02:31.401 --> 02:34.029
sort of like a party, too.

02:34.071 --> 02:36.197
It's called Thanksgiving.

02:34.071 --> 02:36.197
Now, it's true we're

02:36.239 --> 02:38.283
not a bunch of friends

02:36.239 --> 02:38.283
you just met last week.

02:38.325 --> 02:40.201
We're only the people

02:38.325 --> 02:40.201
